{{DISPLAYTITLE:Hard Combat Achievements}}
[[File:Combat Achievements - hard tier icon.png|left]]
'''Hard [[Combat Achievements]]''' tasks require the player to have high combat levels, having high-level equipment available, and an intermediate knowledge of dealing with boss mechanics in order to complete. Stamina-type tasks begin to appear as well, and the first [[raid]] task appears in the hard tier.
__TOC__
==Requirements==
; Items
{{Checklist|
*Any [[demonbane weapon]]
*Any variation of the {{plink|angler outfit|pic=Angler hat}}
*{{plink|Brittle key}} to access the [[Grotesque Guardians]]
*{{plink|Dark totem}} for every kill attempt at [[Skotizo]] (at least 5)
*{{plink|Hespori seed}} for every successful [[Hespori]] kill (at least 5)
}}
; Skills
{{Checklist|
*{{SCP|Agility|70|link=yes}}{{Boostable|no}} to access [[Saradomin's Encampment]]
*{{SCP|Farming|65|link=yes}} to access [[Hespori]]
*{{SCP|Firemaking|50|link=yes}} to subdue the [[Wintertodt]]
*{{SCP|Fishing|35|link=yes}} to subdue [[Tempoross]]
*{{SCP|Hitpoints|70|link=yes}}{{Boostable|no}} to access [[Zamorak's Fortress]]
*{{SCP|Ranged|70|link=yes}}{{Boostable|no}} to access [[Armadyl's Eyrie]]
*{{SCP|Slayer|87|link=yes}}{{Boostable|no}}
*{{SCP|Strength|70|link=yes}}{{Boostable|no}} to access [[Bandos' Stronghold]]
}}
; Quests/Favour
{{Checklist|smallindent=yes|notoggleparent=yes|
*60% [[Hosidius]] [[favour]] to access [[Hespori]]
*[[Priest in Peril]] to access the [[Barrows]] minigame
*Partial completion of [[Regicide]] to access [[Zulrah]]
*Partial completion of [[Troll Stronghold]] '''or''' partial completion of [[Death Plateau]] and a [[Ghommal's Hilt]] to access the [[God Wars Dungeon]]
*Completion of [[Enter the Abyss]] or partial completion of [[Fairytale II - Cure a Queen]] to access the Abyssal Nexus}}

